WEBVTT

00:05.330 --> 00:08.197
( theme music playing )

01:53.280 --> 01:54.872
- ( phone ringing )
- ( dog barking )

01:57.080 --> 01:58.308
HEY, MARITA.

01:58.410 --> 02:00.071
NO, I'M WORKING.
( chuckles )

02:00.180 --> 02:03.445
ANOTHER HALF HOUR
AND I GOTI'A GO FEED
A CAT OFF MULHOLLAND.

02:04.890 --> 02:06.448
WHAT KIND OF PARTY?

02:06.560 --> 02:09.188
ALL RIGHT, I'LL CALL YOU
WHEN I GET HOME.

02:11.160 --> 02:12.627
OH, SHIT.

02:12.730 --> 02:14.857
YOU SHOULD SEE
THIS HILL.

02:14.960 --> 02:17.690
NO, I'M ON MY
ROLLERBLADES.

02:17.800 --> 02:20.598
I SHOULD REALLY
TAKE THEM OFF
AND WALK DOWN.

02:20.700 --> 02:22.600
IT'S REALLY STEEP.

02:22.710 --> 02:26.237
REALLY, REALLY STEEP.

02:26.340 --> 02:28.535
CALL YOU RIGHT BACK.

02:30.180 --> 02:31.442
( chuckles )

02:31.550 --> 02:33.609
COME ON, PUP,
COME ON!

02:33.720 --> 02:34.971
WHOO!

02:35.080 --> 02:37.048
ALL RIGHT!

02:37.150 --> 02:39.516
( panting )

02:42.330 --> 02:43.456
OH MY GOD!
NOW WE'RE SAFE.

02:43.560 --> 02:46.893
( grunts )

02:47.000 --> 02:48.922
( panting, whining )

02:51.070 --> 02:52.059
( car door opens,
closes )

02:52.170 --> 02:53.637
( barking )

02:53.740 --> 02:55.594
( man yelling )
I NEED SOME HELP
OUT HERE!

02:57.810 --> 02:58.538
I NEED SOME HELP!

03:06.110 --> 03:07.509
DID I TELL YOU
NATE'S DRAGGING ME

03:07.620 --> 03:09.986
TO A QUAKER CHURCH
SERVICE TONIGHT?

03:10.090 --> 03:11.717
- NO. HUH!
- YEAH.

03:11.820 --> 03:14.209
HE THINKS
COUPLES THERAPY IS
A WASTE OF TIME,

03:14.320 --> 03:16.629
