HIS SOLUTION.

03:16.730 --> 03:19.028
I THOUGHT YOU WERE
ALREADY GOING TO THERAPY.

03:19.130 --> 03:20.950
OH YEAH,
WE WENT ONCE,

03:21.060 --> 03:23.494
BUT HE THOUGHT

03:23.600 --> 03:26.023
THAT THE THERAPIST AND I
WERE GANGING UP ON HIM,

03:26.130 --> 03:27.893
SO THAT WAS THAT.

03:28.000 --> 03:30.707
WELL, WHO KNOWS,
MAYBE A LITTLE SPIRITUALITY
WILL HELP, YOU KNOW.

03:30.810 --> 03:32.232
QUAKERISM?

03:32.340 --> 03:34.103
YEAH, RIGHT.

03:34.210 --> 03:37.600
I JUST WISH HE'D TAKE
HALF AS MUCH INTEREST
IN HIS OWN BABY.

03:37.710 --> 03:39.940
HEY, IF IT WAS
IMPORTANT TO YOU
TO HAVE HIM HERE,

03:40.050 --> 03:41.745
YOU SHOULD HAVE MADE
THAT CLEAR TO HIM.

03:41.850 --> 03:43.738
I DIDN'T TELL HIM.

03:43.850 --> 03:46.978
NATE AND I,
WE'RE 100 MILES APART
ON THIS BABY.

03:47.090 --> 03:48.387
ON EVERYTHING, REALLY.

03:48.490 --> 03:50.879
I DIDN'T WANT HIM HERE.

03:50.990 --> 03:53.049
I MEAN, IT'S NOT
GOOD FOR ME.

03:53.160 --> 03:55.549
IT'S CERTAINLY NOT GOOD
FOR THE BABY.

03:55.660 --> 03:57.969
HUH.

03:58.070 --> 03:59.890
- THANKS FOR COMING.
- YEAH.

04:00.000 --> 04:02.195
- ( knock)
- ( door opens )

04:02.310 --> 04:04.505
- HELLO, BRENDA.
- HEY, DR. MELNICK.

04:04.610 --> 04:06.669
HOW ARE YOU
FEELING TODAY?

04:06.780 --> 04:08.407
OKAY. YEAH.

04:08.510 --> 04:10.603
- WOULD YOU LIE BACK
FOR ME PLEASE?
- MM-HMM.

04:15.020 --> 04:18.012
- NO HUSBAND TODAY?
- NO, NO. HE COULDN'T
GET AWAY FROM WORK.

04:18.120 --> 04:19.712
THIS IS
MY FRIEND JACKIE.

04:34.740 --> 04:36.560
- ( muffled heartbeat)
- THERE'S YOUR FETUS.

04:40.210 --> 04:42.701
OH.

04:42.810 --> 04:44.801
NICE HEARTBEAT.

04:44.910 --> 04:46.844
SIZE LOOKS GOOD.
YEAH.

04:46.950 --> 04:49.942
EVERYTHING SEEMS TO BE
DEVELOPING NORMALLY
AT THIS POINT.

04:50.050 --> 04:51.984
SO THE BABY'S HEALTHY?

04:52.090 --> 04:54.217
