TO DO AN AMNIO.

04:54.320 --> 04:55.514
NO. NO.

04:58.430 --> 05:00.421
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW
THE BABY'S SEX?

05:02.400 --> 05:04.925
HERE'S MY WORK NUMBER,
MY CELL NUMBER--

05:05.030 --> 05:06.361
I KNOW THOSE NUMBERS,
DAVID.

05:06.470 --> 05:08.495
YES, BUT SOMETIMES
IN THE PANIC OF AN EMERGENCY

05:08.600 --> 05:10.306
