WRITTEN DOWN.

05:10.410 --> 05:13.436
I'LL BE DRIVING
ROGER'S LIMO ALL DAY,
SO HERE'S THAT NUMBER.

05:13.540 --> 05:15.371
THIS IS TOO MANY NUMBERS,
HONESTLY.

05:15.480 --> 05:17.675
WE REALLY APPRECIATE YOU
WATCHING THE BOYS.

05:17.780 --> 05:19.577
DURRELL DIDN'T TELL US
UNTIL LAST NIGHT THAT

05:19.680 --> 05:22.148
- IT WAS TEACHER
DEVELOPMENT DAY.
- YOU DIDN'T ASK ME.

05:22.250 --> 05:25.378
'M GLAD TO FINALLY HAVE
SOME TIME WITH MY NEW
GRANDCHILDREN.

05:25.490 --> 05:26.957
YOU'VE BEEN
HIDING THEM FROM ME.

05:27.060 --> 05:29.620
WE'VE BEEN TRYING TO KEEP
THEM TO A REGULAR SCHEDULE.

05:29.730 --> 05:31.027
WELL, WE'LL
HAVE FUN TODAY.

05:31.130 --> 05:32.950
I BROUGHT THE MAKINGS FOR
CHOCOLATE CHIP COOKIES.

05:33.060 --> 05:35.995
- I THOUGHT I'D BAKE.
- I LIKE CHOCOLATE CHIP COOKIES.

05:36.100 --> 05:37.328
ALL BOYS DO.

05:37.430 --> 05:40.137
- I DON'T.
- YOU'LL LIKE MINE.

05:40.240 --> 05:41.764
OH, WE'LL SEE
ABOUT THAT.

05:41.870 --> 05:44.259
DURRELL, YOU DO WHATEVER
MRS. FISHER TELLS YOU TO DO.

05:44.370 --> 05:46.258
WHAT IF SHE TELLS ME
TO JUMP OUT THE WINDOW?

05:46.380 --> 05:49.804
THEY'RE ALLOWED ONE HOUR
OF TELEVISION, ONE HOUR
OF PLAYSTATION

05:49.910 --> 05:52.071
AND THEY CAN TAKE
THEIR SOCCER BALL DOWN
TO THE COURTYARD.

05:52.180 --> 05:54.546
BUT THEY'D BE'I'I'ER
NOT BE KICKING THE BALL
AGAINST THE BUILDING.

05:54.650 --> 05:57.141
