- I DID NOT SAY THAT.

05:57.250 --> 05:59.684
WE'LL BE FINE, REALLY.
YOU TWO GO NOW.

06:03.260 --> 06:05.148
HAVE A GOOD DAY.

06:05.260 --> 06:07.057
David:
I'LL BE HOME BY 5:00.

06:18.140 --> 06:19.835
YOU LOOK
LIKE A WITCH.

06:19.940 --> 06:21.532
I ASSURE YOU I'M NOT.

06:21.640 --> 06:24.609
I DIDN'T SAY YOU WERE.
I SAID YOU LOOK LIKE ONE.

06:27.150 --> 06:29.744
Man on radio:
This is what they made
very efficient.

06:29.850 --> 06:32.887
This is why the Republicans
rely so much on this base.

06:32.990 --> 06:36.528
This is a corporatized
Christian cult situation

06:36.630 --> 06:38.279
where it's about
personal empowerment

06:38.390 --> 06:40.426
which is part of
the Republican agenda--

06:40.530 --> 06:42.293
the neo-contact
cult agenda.

06:42.400 --> 06:43.799
What Ray was talking about--

06:43.900 --> 06:46.789
