a different type of Christian

06:46.900 --> 06:48.436
who I offended--

06:59.250 --> 07:01.639
( mutters )
OH GOD. JESUS.

07:01.750 --> 07:03.308
OW.

07:03.420 --> 07:05.638
( whistles )

07:08.490 --> 07:10.048
( elevator dings )

07:16.430 --> 07:18.022
( elevator dings )

07:23.010 --> 07:27.674
Usted decidiro sobra
la Seora de Guadalupe.

07:27.780 --> 07:29.998
S. Perro con manguillos
de cobre.

07:30.110 --> 07:31.941
Amarillo pulido.

07:32.050 --> 07:33.039
Qu?

07:33.150 --> 07:34.572
El cobre pulido.

07:34.680 --> 07:36.682
Pulido--
PULIDO WHAT?

07:36.790 --> 07:38.542
Pulido--
qu pulido?

07:38.650 --> 07:41.619
Con en el interior
en seda rosada,
en vez de marrn.

07:41.720 --> 07:43.927
POLISHED.
PULIDO, POLISHED.

07:44.030 --> 07:45.827
POLISHED WHAT?

07:45.930 --> 07:48.023
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

07:48.130 --> 07:50.018
Qu dio.

07:50.130 --> 07:51.995
( sighs )

07:53.140 --> 07:54.198
Por favor,
un momento.

07:56.910 --> 07:58.502
IF YOU KNEW THEY
DIDN'T SPEAK ENGLISH,

07:58.610 --> 08:00.373
