TO HANDLE THE INTAKE?

08:00.480 --> 08:01.731
I'M TRYING
TO LEARN SPANISH.

08:01.840 --> 08:03.444
BY USING OUR CLIENTS
AS A CLASSROOM?

08:03.550 --> 08:05.142
I DIDN'T PLAN THIS.
IT WAS A WALK-IN.

08:05.250 --> 08:06.512
I WAS
THE ONLY ONE AVAILABLE.

08:06.620 --> 08:08.975
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED DO
WITH THIS BODY NOW?

08:09.890 --> 08:11.517
YOU WANNA
TAKE OVER FOR ME?

08:11.620 --> 08:14.555
OH, THAT'S RIGHT.
YOU CAN'T.

08:14.660 --> 08:16.821
I ALREADY DID
MOST OF THE WORK.

08:16.930 --> 08:20.149
GREAT. I'M REALLY
IN THE MOOD FOR DEALING
WITH A GRIEVING WIDOWER.

08:20.260 --> 08:21.750
IT'S HER PARENTS.

08:21.860 --> 08:23.828
SHE'S MARRIED,
THEN HER PARENTS
DON'T HAVE THE RIGHT

08:23.930 --> 08:26.467
- TO MAKE THESE DECISIONS.
- I THINK SHE WAS DIVORCED.

08:26.570 --> 08:29.038
- YOU THINK?
- YES, RICO, I THINK.

08:31.810 --> 08:34.574
( speaking Spanish )

08:38.250 --> 08:40.172
- GRACIAS.
- GRACIAS.

08:45.550 --> 08:47.814
UH, ARE YOU REALLY SURE
ABOUT ALL THIS?

08:47.920 --> 08:51.651
- WHAT?
- DIDN'T YOU OVERDO IT
ON THE MERCHANDISE?

08:51.760 --> 08:53.421
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

08:53.530 --> 08:55.953
YOU SOLD THEM
A CASKET FOR $4,000,

08:56.060 --> 08:58.164
YOU ADDED ANOTHER $600
JUST TO SWITCH HANDLES,

08:58.270 --> 09:00.966
THREE GRAND FOR THE MONUMENT,
ANOTHER $400 FOR DOVES.

09:01.070 --> 09:02.662
IT JUST GOES ON.

09:02.770 --> 09:04.761
THIS IS THEIR YOUNGEST
DAUGHTER THERE BURYING.

09:04.870 --> 09:07.202
THE GUY WORKS
IN A MACHINE SHOP.
HE CAN'T AFFORD THIS.

09:07.310 --> 09:09.972
BESIDES LEARNING TO MANGLE
A FEW WORDS IN SPANISH,

09:10.080 --> 09:13.345
MAYBE YOU SHOULD LEARN
SOMETHING ABOUT LATIN
CULTURE AS WELL.

09:13.450 --> 09:15.008
WE HONOR OUR DEAD, NATE.

09:15.120 --> 09:17.884
- AND END UP BROKE
BECAUSE OF IT.
- THAT IS SO RACIST.

09:17.990 --> 09:20.481
HOW AM I BEING RACIST?!
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO SAID
IT'S CULTURAL.

09:20.590 --> 09:24.378
EVERY SINGLE MEMBER
OF THE FAMILY PITCHES IN
AT MOMENTS LIKE THIS.

09:24.490 --> 09:27.129
EVERYONE.
WE TAKE CARE OF EACH OTHER.
NO ONE'S LEFI' BROKE.

09:28.560 --> 09:29.549
I'VE GOT WORK TO DO.

09:31.700 --> 09:33.964
( door opens, closes )

09:34.070 --> 09:37.369
AS YOU CAN SEE WE'VE GOT
A TOP OF THE LINE RETORT

09:37.470 --> 09:39.461
TO THE PRIMARY
AND SECONDARY CHAMBERS--

09:39.570 --> 09:41.504
JUST RE-LINED
LAST YEAR.

09:41.610 --> 09:42.975
FEEL FREE TO LOOK OVER
EVERYTHING.

09:43.080 --> 09:45.275
- YOU'RE ASKING 340,000?
- MM-HMM.

09:45.380 --> 09:46.813
OH, IT'S WORTH
EVERY PENNY, DAVID.

09:46.920 --> 09:48.911
I GET OVER 300 CASES A YEAR.

09:49.020 --> 09:51.386
I COULD HANDLE MORE
IF I ADDED ANOTHER RETORT

09:51.490 --> 09:52.684
WHICH IS EXACTLY
WHAT I WOULD DO

09:52.790 --> 09:54.678
IF I WERE 20 YEARS
YOUNGER.

09:54.790 --> 09:57.850
- CREMATION IS A GROWING
BUSINESS, YOU KNOW THAT.
- YES, I DO.

09:57.960 --> 10:00.326
YOU DON'T WANT FISHER & SONS
TO GET LEFT BEHIND.

10:00.430 --> 10:02.352
UH, FISHER & DIAZ.

10:02.460 --> 10:04.121
PFFI'.

10:04.230 --> 10:07.529
I'VE GOT ANOTHER
PROSPECTIVE BUYER STOPPING BY
IN THE MORNING.

10:07.640 --> 10:09.835
- I SEE.
- I'M NOT TRYING
TO PUSH YOU,

10:09.940 --> 10:13.307
BUT I'VE HAD THIS PLACE
SINCE 1972.

10:13.410 --> 10:15.037
IT'S BEEN GOOD TO ME.

10:15.140 --> 10:18.871
I'D BE PLEASED
TO PASS IT ON TO THE SONS
OF NATHANIEL FISHER.

10:20.520 --> 10:22.272
I'LL TALK
TO MY PARTNERS.

10:22.380 --> 10:24.712
REGULAR NON-FAT LATI'E.

10:24.820 --> 10:27.459
OH! STEAL US
A BUNCH OF SPLENDAS.

10:27.560 --> 10:29.949
- LIKE A WHOLE BUNCH.
- SPLENDA.

10:30.060 --> 10:32.858
YEAH. A LARGE MOCHA
ICE-BLENDED PLEASE.

10:34.530 --> 10:39.229
I WANT A REGULAR SOY
POMEGRANATE BLUEBERRY
TEA LATI'E

10:39.330 --> 10:44.108
