AND THEN COULD YOU JUST
FILL UP THE REST WITH SOY?

10:44.210 --> 10:48.032
ISN'T THAT JUST
A LARGE SOY POMEGRANATE
BLUEBERRY TEA LA'ITE?

10:48.140 --> 10:50.870
NO, IT'S A REGULAR
IN A LARGE CUP.

10:52.410 --> 10:54.275
OH, AND ALSO...

10:54.380 --> 10:56.177
A REDUCED-FAT...

10:56.280 --> 10:57.713
WHOLESOME MORNING MUFFIN.

11:08.200 --> 11:10.020
CLAIRE?

11:10.130 --> 11:11.722
HEY, ANITA.

11:11.830 --> 11:14.936
WELL, SOMEONE'S
VERY THIRSTY.

11:15.040 --> 11:16.962
- OH.
- AND ON HER WAY
TO BIBLE CLASS, I'M GUESSING.

11:17.070 --> 11:19.561
OH YEAH.
IT'S PRE'ITY AWFUL,
ISN'T IT?

11:19.670 --> 11:22.377
