AT THIS PLACE.

11:22.480 --> 11:24.004
OH, IS THAT WHERE
YOU'VE BEEN?

11:24.110 --> 11:26.476
SHIT, I'VE LEFI' YOU
LIKE 100 MESSAGES.
I THOUGHT YOU WERE DEAD.

11:26.580 --> 11:28.070
( sighs )
SORRY.

11:28.180 --> 11:31.684
YOU WERE LIKE MY BEST FRIEND
AND THEN SUDDENLY
YOU WERE GONE.

11:31.790 --> 11:34.418
( sighs )
WELL, HOW'VE YOU BEEN?

11:34.520 --> 11:36.408
FABULOUS.
YOU KNOW--

11:36.520 --> 11:38.556
SCHOOL, SEX, DRUGS,
CREATING ART.

11:38.660 --> 11:41.652
- WELL, THAT'S GOOD.
- YEAH.

11:41.760 --> 11:44.228
I'M KIND OF ON THE CLOCK,
SO I SHOULD PROBABLY GO.

11:44.330 --> 11:46.730
ALL RIGHT. AH, HERE,
LET ME GIVE YOU THIS.

11:48.600 --> 11:49.908
LAC-ARTS JUNIOR SHOW.

11:50.010 --> 11:53.070
- I GOT A PIECE IN IT.
- OH, WOW.

11:53.180 --> 11:54.909
PLEASE PROMISE
YOU'LL COME.

11:55.010 --> 11:56.477
EVERYBODY'LL BE THERE.

11:58.480 --> 12:00.277
YEAH, OKAY.
GREAT.

12:00.380 --> 12:02.268
GOOD.

12:02.380 --> 12:05.679
Ruth:
BOYS, THE FIRST BATCH
IS READY!

12:05.790 --> 12:08.588
ANTHONY,
DU RRELL,

12:08.690 --> 12:10.055
