12:22.470 --> 12:26.338
( hip-hop music blasting )

12:26.440 --> 12:28.931
( Durrell rapping )

12:29.980 --> 12:31.971
( tires squealing )

12:46.760 --> 12:48.796
I REALLY APPRECIATE
YOU DOING THIS FOR ME.

12:50.170 --> 12:51.899
SURE.

12:52.000 --> 12:54.230
COME ON, A QUAKER
CHURCH SERVICE.

12:54.340 --> 12:56.137
AT THE VERY LEAST
IT'LL BE INTERESTING.

12:56.240 --> 12:58.731
I'M TRYING TO KEEP
AN OPEN MIND.

12:58.840 --> 13:01.104
THERE'S NO SERMON
OR ANYTHING.

13:02.110 --> 13:03.338
PEOPLE JUST SIT SILENTLY

13:03.450 --> 13:05.975
AND WAIT TO BE FILLED
WITH THE PRESENCE OF GOD.

13:08.520 --> 13:11.011
MAGGIE SAYS WE CAN
SAY SOMETHING IF WE
FEEL LIKE IT,

13:11.120 --> 13:13.884
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE TO.
IT'S NOT LIKE A REQUIREMENT.

13:13.990 --> 13:16.857
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE
MAGGIE THINKS WE SHOULD KNOW?

13:20.230 --> 13:22.698
MELNICK SAYS THE BABY'S
LOOKING REALLY GOOD.

13:22.800 --> 13:25.291
- WHEN WAS THIS?
- THIS MORNING.

13:25.400 --> 13:27.038
I HAD A SONOGRAM.

13:27.140 --> 13:28.869
WHAT? WHY DIDN'T YOU
TELL ME ABOUT IT?

13:28.970 --> 13:30.699
BECAUSE I WANTED
TO SPARE YOU THE GRIEF.

13:30.810 --> 13:33.278
I'M SORRY, BUT THIS
IS ONE OF THE THINGS
THAT WE TALKED ABOUT.

13:33.380 --> 13:36.076
IT PISSES ME OFF
WHEN YOU DO STUFF LIKE
THIS WITHOUT TELLING ME.

13:36.180 --> 13:38.273
SO WHY DON'T YOU SIT THERE
AND ALLOW YOURSELF

13:38.380 --> 13:40.371
TO BE FILLED
WITH THE PRESENCE OF GOD?

13:44.920 --> 13:48.788
- SO WHAT DID SHE SAY?
- SHE SAID THAT THE BABY
WAS DEVELOPING NORMALLY.

13:48.890 --> 13:51.950
THERE'S NO SIGN
OF ANY IRREGULARITIES,

13:52.060 --> 13:54.722
ALL OF WHICH IS VERY
VERY ENCOURAGING.

13:54.830 --> 13:56.821
SO IT'S PERFECT LY HEALTHY.

13:56.930 --> 13:59.069
WELL, YOU KNOW,
THERE ARE SOME THINGS

13:59.170 --> 14:01.058
THAT THE SONOGRAM
CAN'T TELL.

14:02.370 --> 14:05.168
WHAT, SO IT COULD HAVE
DOWN'S OR SPINA BIFIDA?

14:05.270 --> 14:08.535
