SO, GREAT!

14:14.080 --> 14:16.446
WE GET TO MAYBE CHECK
THIS ONE THING OFF THE LIST

14:16.550 --> 14:18.780
AND IT COULD STILL HAVE
A MILLION OTHER THINGS
WRONG WITH IT.

14:18.890 --> 14:21.358
THE BABY'S NOT AN IT,
NATE, IT'S A GIRL.

14:23.690 --> 14:25.282
